# Socket Security: Add VFS and binject sources to node.gyp
#
# This patch integrates Socket Security's VFS and binject framework source files
# into the Node.js build system, including C/C++ sources and include directories.
#
# CRITICAL: This patch must include ALL binject C/C++ source files to resolve
# linker errors. The build system compiles node_sea_smol.cc which calls binject
# C functions (binject_batch, smol_config_init, vfs_utils, etc.), so all
# implementation files must be linked into the Node.js binary.
#
# Files included:
# - Socket Security sea-smol wrapper (node_sea_smol.cc) - bridges Node.js to binject C API
# - Socket Security VFS binding (node_vfs.cc) - Node.js VFS integration
# - binject core (binject.c) - main CLI and format detection
# - binject LIEF implementations (elf_inject_lief.cpp, macho_inject_lief.cpp, pe_inject_lief.cpp) - LIEF-based injection
# - binject platform implementations (elf_inject.c, pe_inject.c, macho_inject_lief_wrapper.c) - native implementations
# - binject utilities (smol_config.c, vfs_config.c, vfs_utils.c, stub_repack.c, elf_pe_cross_platform.c, remove_signature_lib.c)
# - build-infra dependencies (tar_create.c, gzip_compress.c, file_io_common.c, file_utils.c) - VFS archiving and I/O
# - bin-infra dependencies (compression_common.c, binary_format.c, smol_segment.c, smol_segment_reader.c, stub_smol_repack_lief.cpp) - compression, binary format and repacking
#
# Compression Library Dependencies:
# - macOS: libcompression (native Apple Compression framework) for gzip_compress.c and compression_common.c
# - Linux/Windows: LZFSE (deps/lzfse/lzfse.gyp:liblzfse) for compression_common.c
# - Linux/Windows: libdeflate (deps/libdeflate/libdeflate.gyp:libdeflate) for gzip_compress.c
# - CRITICAL: libcompression must be added to ALL targets that link libnode.a on macOS.
#   libnode.a contains gzip_compress.o and compression_common.o, so all executables linking libnode.a
#   need the library at link time to resolve compression symbols.
#
# Targets modified:
# - Main node target: Added binject sources (node_use_lief condition) + libcompression (libraries section)
# - cctest target: Added libcompression for libnode.a symbols
# - embedtest target: Added libcompression for libnode.a symbols
# - node_mksnapshot target: Added libcompression for libnode.a symbols
#
# Files modified:
# - node.gyp: Add binject and VFS source files, include directories, and libcompression
#
--- a/node.gyp	2026-02-06 08:59:59
+++ b/node.gyp	2026-02-06 09:00:34
@@ -694,6 +694,12 @@
             'Ws2_32.lib',
